<row>
<entry valign="top" align="left" namest="c1" nameend="c2"><emphasis effect="bold">Chapter Objectives:</emphasis><newline/>
<list id="fs-idm391035520" list-type="bulleted">
<item>Students will be able to identify and evaluate the causes of the Declaration of Independence.</item>
<item>Students will be able to evaluate the causes and effects of key events in the Revolutionary War.</item>
<item>Students will be able to compare various perspectives on constitutional principles and assess arguments surrounding the structure of the new Union under the Constitution.</item>
</list></entry>
</row>
